headline: PulteGroup (PHM): Assessing Valuation After Pending Home Sales and Mortgage Rate Trends Boost Sector Optimism
summary: PulteGroup (PHM) has been on investors' radar this week, outperforming peers as homebuilder stocks picked up momentum.
